This paper deals with video reconstruction using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.MM) and image alignment (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper discusses the practicality of the proposed approach, which could fall under robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
